    "body" : "<p>They represent <code>[</code> and <code>]</code>. The encoding is called <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Percent-encoding\" rel=\"noreferrer\">\"URL encoding\"</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
