    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Well it's the usual <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Url_encoding\" rel=\"noreferrer\">url encoding</a> </p>\n\n<p>So they stand for <code>[</code>, respectively <code>]</code></p>\n"
